BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 526.89 Td (7168], block scales for every 128 hidden elements, FP8 local expert weights for 32 experts, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 513.89 Td (corresponding block-scale tensors. The first expert matrix has shape [32, 4096, 7168], where the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 500.89 Td (output dimension is the concatenation of gate and up projections. The second matrix has shape [32,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 487.89 Td (7168, 2048]. The output is BF16 with shape [T, 7168].) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 470.89 Td (The routing rule matches the reference semantics. For each token, the score used for selection is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 457.89 Td (sigmoid\(logit\) + bias. The 256 experts are divided into eight groups of 32 experts; each group is) Tj ET
