BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 431.89 Td (eight experts are selected within the retained groups. The combination weights are not computed from) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 418.89 Td (the biased scores. They are computed from the unbiased sigmoid values on the selected experts,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 405.89 Td (normalized by their sum, and multiplied by routed_scaling_factor. Only experts in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 392.89 Td ([local_expert_offset, local_expert_offset + 32\) are evaluated on this rank.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 375.89 Td (The essential performance challenge is routing-induced irregularity. The number of local routed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 362.89 Td (tokens varies by expert and by input length, yet the arithmetic work inside each expert is a large) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 349.89 Td (matrix multiplication with FP8 block dequantization. An efficient design must preserve expert) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.60 Tf 48.00 336.89 Td (sparsity while presenting the GEMM stages with regular memory access and contiguous row ranges.) Tj ET
